Author: fatxdiannee
Text: That’s funny because the ones I take like make me dry heave if I take them when fasting. So I try to only have them if I binge or something.

Author: akatsuki_no_bun
Text: Not gunna lie, some diet pills make me super hungry. I don’t know how that’s physiologically possible but the number of times they have completely derailed my day is too high.
